com.madrobot.ui.widgets

Class WebImageView

  • java.lang.Object
    • ViewSwitcher
      • com.madrobot.ui.widgets.WebImageView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TaskNotifier

    public class WebImageView
extends ViewSwitcher
implements TaskNotifier
    An image view that fetches its image off the web using the supplied URL. While the image is being downloaded, a progress indicator will be shown.

    Styled Attributes

    • imageUrl(string): URL for the image to be downloaded
    • autoLoad(boolean): Flag to indicate if the image should be downloaded automatically or should be user initiated loadImage()
    • progressDrawable(drawable): Drawable to be used while the image is loaded. if the ProgressBar is not desired.
    • errorDrawable(drawable):Drawable to be used if the image could not be loaded.
